		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="404" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">璇蛸轻轻地扒拉两下，依次造成<span color="#7fbfff">40%,<br/>60%</span><span>伤害，容易后接「洄水飞浪」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="398" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">璇蛸划拉转圈袭来，持续造成<span color="#7fbfff">20%</span><span>伤害，最后用力再转一圈，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">璇蛸突然朝玩家袭来，用力砸一下，造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="425" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">璇蛸展开半径<span color="#ffdfbf">15m</span><span>的</span><span textDecoration="underline">蕴光领域</span><span>，朝玩家方向斩出两道水刃，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">璇蛸展开半径<span color="#ffdfbf">15m</span><span>的</span><span textDecoration="underline">蕴光领域</span><span>，并且朝玩家钻旋袭来，途径造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">30%</span><span>伤害，行至目标处释放水涌，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
