		<RichText x="66" y="912" width="443" height="154" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蕴光领域：展开时施加「蕴光之茧」状态，扣除全队角色<span color="#ffdfbf">10%+1800</span><span>点生命值，若角色生命值低于</span><span color="#ffdfbf">7200</span><span>点，则改为扣除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">35%</span><span>生命值，可致命但可开大招躲避；主动治疗清除后获得「出缠」效果。若范围内前台角色仍处于「蕴光之茧」状态，璇蛸则不会施放「断浪长袭」、「露流彩沫」。<br/>蕴光之茧：暴击率</span><span color="#ffdfbf">-10%</span><span>，造成的伤害</span><span color="#ffdfbf">-10%</span><span>，受治疗加成</span><span color="#ffdfbf">-10%</span><span>。<br/>出缠：暴击率</span><span color="#ffdfbf">+15%</span><span>，造成的伤害</span><span color="#ffdfbf">+50%</span><span>，持续15s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
	</Group>
</Graphic>